    dc:description "FIGURE 12. Field images of: (a–b) Protosticta cyanofemora sp. nov. (a) male; (b) female; (c–d) P. myristicaensis sp. nov. (c) male; (d) female. Photos: (a, c–d) SJ, & (b) KAS." ;
