    dc:description "FIGURE 8. Protosticta myristicaensis sp. nov. Paratype males: (a–b) NCBS-BM655, (c–f) NCBS-BM654: (a) prothorax, dorsal view; (b) caudal appendages, ventral view; (c) face; (d) pterostigma of right FW; (e) caudal appendages, lateral view; (f) caudal appendages, dorsal view." ;
